{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I would find parks, which were kind of secluded and deserted, and spend hours in parks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I had to do something with myself for a whole day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That was tough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But I did it day after day after day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did-- well, I had money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I got money from when I left the house, my mother gave me some money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I made a lot of money on that asphalt business, which I kept doing, even after I was uncovered once.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got just a new truck, and I kept doing it with new truckers, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was a very profitable business it so happens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because anything which had to do with the black market was extremely profitable.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Part of that business was also, as-- as we were traveling in that truck, this distance from Lwow to Warsaw is probably 300 miles.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it took like a whole night, or a whole day's travel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So on the way, we had to stop in a few places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we would stop in villages, and buy flour.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The farmers would sell flour, all on the black market, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we would buy that flour, and then sell it in the city, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was profitable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it was a profitable business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I made money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I know that I had a couch like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the whole couch, the floor was 500-- the highest bill, was the nomination was 500 zloty.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I had packets of these 500 zloty laying in that couch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "As a matter of fact-- and that's a side story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was looking to exchange these zlotys for dollars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was willing to buy it from a black marketeer.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
